summary: Have you ever thought that it sucks to have to start a whole new campaign without the awesomeness of your Daedric Crescent or the annoyance of your Staff of Everscamp? Does the thought that you will never again see these great items drive you mad? Well your in luck!
descriptionHtml:
This mod is a list of all artifacts that were not added to Skyrim and links to nexus modders\' pages that contain them. None of the work is my own, I simply organized it for you.

If you have posted a mod featuring one or more of the artifacts, by all means message me and you will find your link on here in no time. Duplicates are excepted; it gives players options.

If you wish to submit an item, please insure that the stats, enchantment, and look of the item matches or is similar with past games. These are supposed to be as Lore Friendly as possible. (Obviously the Dragonborn wouldn\'t be the Nareverine so couldn\'t wear the Moon-and-Star)


The format of the list has been changed. Instead of it appearing in the description, it is now a word document with hyperlinks so you don\'t have to copy and paste the urls.
